'Ibrahimovic is one of the best players in the world with Messi and Ronaldo,' Van der Meyde told Goal.com.

'He is such a big and strong guy. He can be an intimidating figure. Plus he has amazing technique as well for someone with a big body like his.

'He's the type of player who wants to win at all costs. He is arrogant, but that's him. It's a positive sort of arrogance if you ask me. He is a true great.'

